Package House

Class HouseLayout.RoomLayout

java.lang.Object
House.HouseLayout.RoomLayout
Enclosing class:
HouseLayout
public class HouseLayout.RoomLayout
extends java.lang.Object
Inner class modeling the RoomLayout entity. This class is used to parse out the JSON contents of a house layout file, for each room.
